name: The Alias - Prison Identities
description:
The Alias- Prison Identities
Prison Identities - The Alias,  a convicted female prisoner with no mug shot. There are records of Mary Woodman,also having many other names along with this various crimes. Even though Mary does have a criminal record there are no mug shots of her nor any descriptions of what she may of looked like. To highlight this lack of identity I have given her no face, just a name. 

This is part of the Prison Residencies project at Shepton Mallet Prison, UK 18/09/2021 - 03/10/2021. This collage uses real records of female prisoners from the UK Victorian era. The facial image is completely made up only influenced by the historical records.
